data.description: **ASSUMABLE VA LOAN**    WELCOME HOME! This beautiful, well maintained home is perfect! It has 4 large bedrooms, all of which are on the second floor and 2.5 bathrooms. The sellers are interested in selling the property with all the furniture, electronics and appliances included which makes the home ideal for a vacation rental. 3 of the 4 bedrooms have beds and mounted televisions. There is a opportunity A must-see!
